 Episode 2 of Shutter Speed’s comedy web series “Rofia Tailor Loran (RTL)” has finally premiered, and in this episode, Rofia and Lape have picked a name and begun designing the space for Rofia’s fashion business. “RTL” is about a small-time tailor (Rofia) who comes to the city to find greener pastures. She connects with an old friend, a supposed city big gal, (Lape) and together they navigate the murky waters of friendship and business. In this series, Bimbo Ademoye and Bolaji Ogunmola give a stellar performance alongside a host of cameo appearances. The series is produced and directed by Biodun Stephen. Enjoy! 